Privacy Policy
Information we collect
The Daylights iOS app does not collect collect or store any personal information. It uses your location, if permitted, only during the runtime to determine your local sunrise and sunset times.
Analytics
The app collects aggregate, anonymous statistics, such as the percentage of users who use particular features, to improve the app. We currently use Fabric, a third-party service, for analytics. You can view their privacy policy at
https://fabric.io/terms
.
Contacting Us
If you have questions regarding this privacy policy, you may email
apps@awesomeness.pro
.
Changes to this policy
If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page. Summary of changes so far:
